92 template<typename other_id_t = long>
93 bool operator==(const PiercedKernelRange<other_id_t> &rhs) const
94 {
95 if (m_cbegin == rhs.m_cbegin) {
96 return false;
97 }
98
99 if (m_cend == rhs.m_cend) {
100 return false;
101 }
102
103 return true;
104 }
105
109 template<typename other_id_t = long>
110 bool operator!=(const PiercedKernelRange<other_id_t> &rhs) const
111 {
112 if (m_cbegin == rhs.m_cbegin) {
113 return true;
114 }
115
116 if (m_cend != rhs.m_cend) {
117 return true;
118 }
119
120 return false;
121 }
122
123protected:
125 const_iterator m_cbegin;

128 const_iterator m_cend;
